  +files/bind-libxml2-2.8.x.patch:
  Fix libxml2 detection, bug 425170, thanks to Bruno <bonbons67@internet.lu>.

  27 Jul 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> bind-9.9.1_p2.ebuild:
  Stable arm, bug #427966

