  -files/localhost, -files/named.conf-r1, -files/named.conf-r2,
  -bind-9.3.2_beta2.ebuild, +bind-9.3.2_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  Cleaned out unused files, bug #108123 fixed only in 9.3.2_beta2 for now.

